{
  "id": "adv_card_szk_06_01",
  "title": "兵藤雫",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "雫、お疲れ様\n一人でどうしたんだ？",
      "startTime": 2.8666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2530.0000000000005,
          "startTime": 3.33
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2833.3333332999996,
          "startTime": 3.6333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん、今度のライブ\n私の家族も観に来てくれる、って……！",
      "startTime": 8.977029562,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "星見まつりのステージにか？",
      "startTime": 12.7103628953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.1123810529
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "うん……そう、それ\n早速、お母さんに連絡したら",
      "startTime": 17.9457143862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "家族で観に行く、応援してる、って\nさっき……メッセ、来てた",
      "startTime": 25.045715022,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.7790483553
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "地元のライブは久しぶりだし\n家族が来てくれるなんて……凄く、楽しみ",
      "startTime": 30.5758724231,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.1790483553
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "やる気十分だな\n俺も、星見でのライブは特別に感じるよ",
      "startTime": 37.4333339691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.5602276562
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "星見市から始まった、サニピが\nいろんな経験を積んで……",
      "startTime": 43.3935609895,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "星見まつりという、舞台に立つ……\n凄く、エモい……！",
      "startTime": 49.5935609895,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.460225113
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "ファンの人達だけじゃなくて、地元の人達も\nいっぱい観に来てくれると思うと、嬉しい……",
      "startTime": 55.460225113,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな、オファーを受けて良かったよ\nかわりにオフが先になってしまったが",
      "startTime": 62.6666647593,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.6846696295
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫。いつも沢山の人に応援してもらえて\n元気をもらってるから",
      "startTime": 70.4846696295,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.5180029628
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "私は、精一杯歌って、踊るだけ\n星見まつりのMCは、ちょっと心配だけど……",
      "startTime": 77.6846696295,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうなのか？　MCはライブで何度もやってるし\n大丈夫だと思うけどな",
      "startTime": 85.8276529448,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.9840574977
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "地元となると、やっぱり、緊張する……\nお父さんとお母さんに、いいところ見せたいし",
      "startTime": 93.017390831,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.2840574977
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ変に気負わず、いつも通りやればいいと思うぞ",
      "startTime": 97.2840574977,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "雫は前より、話すのだってうまくなってる\n成長した姿を見せれば、家族も喜んでくれるさ",
      "startTime": 104.5534085311,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.5440576629
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "そう、かな……うん、そうだといいな……\n早く、お祭りの日にならないかな",
      "startTime": 114.3773909963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数ヶ月後",
      "startTime": 118.9107243296,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 119.9107243296
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "……うーーん……\n…………うーーーーん……",
      "startTime": 124.0648519766,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "やけに唸ってるな……どうしたんだ？\n星見まつりに向けたレッスンも大詰めだろう",
      "startTime": 131.6999980926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん……\n実はさっき、サニピのみんなと当日のことを話してて",
      "startTime": 137.3824249661,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "せっかく星見まつりに参加するんだし、ライブの後\nみんなでお祭りを見て回ろう、っていう話になった",
      "startTime": 147.0490916327,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-szk015.m4a",
      "text": "実家も近いし、浴衣を取ってきて\nみんなで着ることになったんだけど……",
      "startTime": 155.3157582994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "いいじゃないか。浴衣を着てお祭りを回るなんて\n想像するだけでも楽しそうだ",
      "startTime": 161.9999980926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-szk016.m4a",
      "text": "うん、みんなでお祭りを回って、花火を見て……\n最後に流星群を見て……絶対、楽しい",
      "startTime": 169.9086833393,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-szk017.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、みんなが盛り上がってたから\n言い出せなかったけど……私、浴衣って持ってない……",
      "startTime": 178.6420156553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-szk018.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくみんなと遊べるのに、一人だけ私服なの\n想像したら……ちょっと寂しくて……",
      "startTime": 189.9220179266,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（そうか……アイドルになる前の雫は）\n（あんまり友達と遊ぶようなことがなかったから……）",
      "startTime": 197.5000031788,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、今からでも買ったらどうだ？\n忙いようなら、通販で頼む手もあると思うぞ",
      "startTime": 204.0017626862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-szk019.m4a",
      "text": "通販……そうだね、早めに出荷してもらえるとこなら\nまだ、間に合うかも",
      "startTime": 213.0724982017,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-szk020.m4a",
      "text": "サニピのみんなと行く、星見まつりで\n浴衣デビュー……ドキドキしてきた……！",
      "startTime": 218.4724982017,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "ちなみに、ステージで着る衣装も\n浴衣風のデザインになる予定だよ",
      "startTime": 224.7373415543,
      "sfxList": []
